summary: A mod that improves the texture and look of the vanilla weapons, including staffs, swords, greatswords, warhammers, bow and arrows, daggers, and war axes, Those are the only weapons I know ... I don't know if there is more.
descriptionHtml: A mod that improves the look, and texture of the vanilla weapons, It also increases the damage on swords and daggers, like a damage 8 dagger will go up to a 12 damage dagger, stuff like that, (maybe). Â  :)
